title: Oracles of Nostradamas - Charles A. Ward [EN PDF]
description:
Oracles of Nostradamas

by Charles A. Ward

World events are rapidly catching up with the prophecies made by Nostradamas
three hundred years ago. Whether his predictions were accidental or based upon
an occult foreknowledge, they are frequently uncanny in their accuracy.
His book of oracles is having a tremendous vogue at present, partly because of
wide variety of interpretations that can be made from his prognostications, but mainly
because it makes fascinating reading when related to catastrophes announced daily while
the world is in crisis.
This edition edited by Charles A. Ward gives special emphasis to prophecies of contemporary
events and those immediately ahead.
